是对社会诚信体系的挑衅。同时，造假带来的市场竞争机制扭曲，还将让整个行业陷入信任危机。 在网络空间，学历并不是衡量作品的唯一标准。不少网红主播就曾在直播中回应网友关于其学历、经历的问题，虽然没有光鲜靓丽的学历和阅历，但普通人的奋斗故事同样能收获大量粉丝。用诚信、真诚赢得的关注和粉丝，远比虚构人设来得更牢靠。千万网红被指学历造假，诚信比人设更重要"},"attached_info":"CkAIipayiK/Ikrg9EAMaCTExMTE1ODcyOSCP07a4BjAAOOkFQBZyCTkyMTA1ODIzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"41 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dfea286a2a5506f0c550fa9a79381461_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1729047666.57601","card_id":"Q_530882777","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":530882777,"title":"为什么感觉《潜伏》里余则成当了副站长和之前一样没什么权力威信？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/530882777","type":"question","created":1651372900,"answer_count":118,"follower_count":511,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,8412,47110,100782,144837],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"反而李涯才好像个副站长，可以暗中监视，抓余则成，后面继续搜黑料，按理说这么对领导不早死很多回了吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IipayiK/Ikrg9EAMaCDgwMjU2MjQ0IOTmt5MGMAA4/wNAF3IJNTMwODgyNzc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"39 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8a055714ea02b2be4c39596d1823abb5_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1729047666.57865","card_id":"Q_946498418","target":{"id":946498418,"title":"离岸人民币一度跌破 7.13 关口，日内贬值逾 350 点，发生了什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/946498418","type":"question","created":1728978199,"answer_count":158,"follower_count":485,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids